# EXIT PRICE WORKFLOW & WIN/LOSS TRACKING

This update replaces manual P/L entry with an automated system based on your **Exit Price**, ensuring more accurate accounting and a clearer visual of your performance.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Exit Price Calculation:** When closing a trade, you will now enter the **Giá chốt (Exit Price)**. The system will automatically calculate your profit/loss based on the price difference and your trade volume.
> - **Long:** `Profit = Volume * (Exit - Entry)`
> - **Short:** `Profit = Volume * (Entry - Exit)`

> [!NOTE]
> **Status Badges:** A new column will be added to the journal to clearly mark each closed trade as **WIN** or **LOSS**.

